description: Trumpeter Randy Brecker talks about the Brecker Brothers and how the band was originally created and also about the most recent incarnation.  This "In Person with JazzTimes" interview was done aboard the MS Westerdam during the Jazz Cruise 2012. A longtime regular on the Jazz Cruise, Brecker performed both as an All-Star and as a solo artist. Interview by Irene Lee. Video by Lee Mergner.  Footage shot on Canon EOS 5D Mark II.
title: Randy Brecker on the Brecker Brothers Reunion Project
